injured. 
</P>
<P>
 The fire occurred at the Chaparral apartment complex at 1221 N. State College 
Boulevard. 
</P>
<P>
 When firefighters arrived at the scene just after 1 a.m., four carports in the 
apartment complex were burning. 
</P>
<P>
 It took 37 firefighters about 10 minutes to contain the blaze, the spokesman 
said. 
</P>
<P>
 No dwellings were damaged in the blaze. 
