 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Joe Roussel: 0-0 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. 
HGT. P Chris Goodwin Sr. 6-1 G Ryan Villmer Sr. 6-4 C 04,15,05,06,04 TOP 
RETURNERS YR. HGT. P Javier Barron Sr. 5-8 G Ahad Lakhani Sr. 6-4 C Seijin Lee 
Sr. 6-0 F Chris Smith Sr. 5-11 G Ryan Whieldon Sr. 6-1 F 04,15,05,06,04 TOP 
