<P>
 For the Record: The Streetsmart column Oct. 31 incorrectly listed the opening 
date of a five-mile segment of car-pool lane on the Riverside Freeway in Los 
Angeles County between the San Gabriel River Freeway and the Orange County 
line. The segment will open this month. 
